message.content:
"That little beast Robbie flung yard open six
months afore while Penelope was refitting in the
dockyard and now Kat she's ready for sea he goes
sick. Just because he's an Honourable he can do
what he likes. Anyway, why pick on you to succeed
him?" John didn't answer. There was no point
in stating his discomfort with Peggy.
